Imibiko iveza ukuthi ngezikhathi zehora lesithathu ntambama abaqaphi basolwandle bathole umbiko othi, kunabalisa abathathu asebemuke nolwandle iTiger Beach okuwulwandle okungabhukudwa kulona. INhloko ebambile ophikweni lwezokuxhumana kumasipala, uMnuz Mandla Nsele ithe abaqaphi bathole umbiko ngala madoda amathathu okuthiwa kade ebhukuda olwandle babe sebenikela khona bakwazi ukuwathola lama doda womathathu. “Babe sebenikezwa usizo lokuqala kwatholakala ukuthi ababili kubona sebeshonile. Omunye ube esephuthunyiswa esibhedlela i-Prince Mshiyeni Memorial, nalapho okutholakale ukuthi isimo sakhe asisibi kangako.,”kusho Nsele. Umasipala ube sewucela abantu abahambela olwandle ukuthi bangabhukudi ezindaweni lapho kungabhukudwa khona. - Intatheli yeSolezwe